title: Tane Edmed
text: Tane Edmed (born in <a href="Australia">Australia</a>) is an Australian <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player who plays for the in <a href="Super%20Rugby">Super Rugby</a>. His playing position is <a href="Fly-half%20%28rugby%20union%29">fly-half</a>. He was named in the Waratahs squad for the <a href="2021%20Super%20Rugby%20AU%20season">2021 Super Rugby AU season</a>. He previously represented the in the <a href="2019%20National%20Rugby%20Championship">2019 National Rugby Championship</a>.
